    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      FAILED
      Price change failed probably due to lost communication with pump.
      IDLE
      No prices pending or price change completed successfully
      INVALID_PRICE
      Unable to change price due to price being invalid
      PENDING
      A price change is pending and will be applied when possible
      RUNNING
      A price change is currently running
